sequenceDiagram
    participant M as Model
    participant E as edit tool
    participant L as LSP client
    participant S as Language server
    M->>E: edit(file, old, new)
    E->>E: apply text replace
    E->>L: touchFile(filePath, waitForDiagnostics=true)
    L->>S: publishDiagnostics request
    Note over L,S: blocks up to 3s
    S-->>L: diagnostics list
    L-->>E: diagnostics
    E->>E: filter severity==1 (errors)
    E-->>M: tool output<br/>"edit summary\n\nDiagnostics:\n<errors>"
    Note over M: Model sees errors immediately<br/>and can fix in next step
